Package: callDensity
Type: Package
Title: Analysis for bioacoustic call density estimation (ABCDE)
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Brian S Miller, Danielle Harris, Franciele R Castro, and Nat Kelly
Maintainer: Brian S Miller <Brian.Miller@aad.gov.aut>
Description: Software for estimating the density of animal vocalisations (calls)
    This package includes functions for estimating call density of animal 
    sounds, especially those of low-frequency baleen whales, by applying 
    the algorithms described by Danielle Harris. In particular these algorithms 
    can be used to estimate call density using auxiliary information to estimate
    the probability of detection within an area. The specific auxiliary 
    information required by this package comes from the sonar equation, 
    specifically, distributions of source levels (SL), transmission losses (TL),
    and noise levels (NL). 
